## Keybinds

### Volume Control
bindsym $mod+o exec amixer -q set Master 5%- && killall -SIGUSR1 i3status
bindsym $mod+p exec amixer -q set Master 5%+ && killall -SIGUSR1 i3status

### Open Programs
bindsym $mod+b exec firefox
